name: Simulman 11: Jailhouse Rock
overview: A 2D action adventure written by Natale Fietta and Stefano Balzani for Simulmondo it Europe in 1994. This month's adventure, the installment "Jailhouse Rock" is the door of maximum security prison from where Simulman suspects, our foes are leaving orders for the worst crimes committed in the city. Under false credentials, our agent, yes will have to infiltrate inside the virtual prison ...
